        enough to get your child into the college of her choice? Your child is
        likely to need your help finding the right balance between challenging
        academic classes and electives that help him pursue his interests and
        stay engaged in school. Make sure you're in the loop when your student
        chooses next year's classes so he can realize his dreams.
